text: Nazarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Novochebenkinsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 69 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Isyangulovo, 16 km from Ishemgul. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Nazarovo, Zianchurinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
